column5: It's late I know but good morning Lew!
And G'day to you too Roy  Been sitting here lookin out the window for about 3 hours just wating for the rest of the world to wake up.  Sure is breezy out there !!!!
Morn,n fellas. Cold and blown an trying real hard to snow here.  Weather alert for 40 cm by tonight.
Mornin!  Good to know someone's holding the fort..
Winds West 25km/h here getting drizzle. Everything is coated with ice...gunna have to put out some food for the little chirpin' friends so they don't bust their beaks looking for seeds and whatnot.

The seeds are easy for them, its the whatnots that give them a hard time.I bought  some whatnots somewhere on special this fall. read the instructions Roy. It tells you hownot to use whatnots and where.
Snowin like a bugger up here. Icey as hell this morning.. hope the youngest made it to Barrie to work okay this morning at 7!

Still real breezy around these parts with the odd snow flake thrown in and just to be on the safe side,  I had the winter tires put on this morning.  Been working outside for the last couple hours and   the cool temps make doin chores alot easier than the hot steamy summer we just went thru, and with all the leaves gone it sure makes trimming trees that much simpler.
Chilly - But the sun is shining here.  Balmy 39 Degrees F.
